00:13:11,540 --> 00:13:13,600
<i>(roar)</i>

261
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:14,930
Second place!

262
00:13:14,950 --> 00:13:16,270
We got silver!

263
00:13:21,650 --> 00:13:24,450
Congratulations to
all our medalists.

264
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:26,540
And now, the anthem of--

265
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,790
And I shall do the
honor of singing!

266
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:32,600
<i>(cheers)</i>

267
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:34,890
Spike? What are
you doing?

268
00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:37,150
You know how they always
just play the music?

269
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:39,430
Well, I know all the
words to our anthem

270
00:13:39,580 --> 00:13:42,390
